href="jonmsterling.xml"
type="local"
addr="jonmsterling">Jon Sterling</fr:link></fr:author></fr:authors><fr:parent>jms-00CW</fr:parent></fr:frontmatter><fr:mainmatter><fr:p>A new <fr:code>--assets-dirs</fr:code> option has been added to the <fr:code>forester build</fr:code> command, which can be used to supply multiple directories containing static assets that should be copied into the forest. By default, the option is set to <fr:code>assets</fr:code>.</fr:p></fr:mainmatter></fr:tree><fr:tree
